																																																								<div class="uael-timeline-desc-content"><p>The first epicenter of the virus in the U.S., Seattle restaurants take a hit in the last week of February with some restaurants down as much as 40%, and the overall industry seeing a 10% drop. Online grocery and meal kit sales were the only foodservice category showing growth in the market over the same time period.</p></div> 																																</div>
