																																	<div class="uael-timeline-heading-text">
												<h4 class="uael-timeline-heading">Preliminary Estimates Show 20% of U.S. Restaurants Could Close Permanently</h4> 											</div>
																																																								<div class="uael-timeline-desc-content"><p>According to a UBS note published April 1, <a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/1-in-5-restaurants-could-close-due-to-coronavirus-ubs-2020-4">some 20% of restaurants across the U.S.</a> may not re-open following the coronavirus pandemic. This could mean more than 200,000 restaurants keeping their doors closed and a loss of millions of jobs.</p></div> 																																</div>
