		<item>
		<title>Where is the Food Service Industry Heading?</title>
		<link>https://aaronallen.com/blog/food-service-industry-trends</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Aaron Allen]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2019 22:52:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Insights]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Restaurant Industry]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://aaronallen.com/?p=12838</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>The biggest threats are often those that few see coming. It’s a case of history repeating itself with companies being wiped out by disruptive forces that were often dismissed when they first appeared. A similar fate could be met by many restaurant companies if they do not take active steps to modernize their businesses and &#8230; </p>
<p class="link-more"><a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/food-service-industry-trends" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> "Where is the Food Service Industry Heading?"</span></a></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/food-service-industry-trends">Where is the Food Service Industry Heading?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://aaronallen.com">Aaron Allen &amp; Associates, Global Restaurant Consultants</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="12838" class="elementor elementor-12838">
						<div class="elementor-inner">
				<div class="elementor-section-wrap">
									<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b1bc7e4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="b1bc7e4" data-element_type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
							<div class="elementor-row">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-638768c" data-id="638768c" data-element_type="column">
			<div class="elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated">
							<div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8892bc3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8892bc3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>The biggest threats are often those that few see coming. It’s a case of history repeating itself with companies being wiped out by disruptive forces that were often dismissed when they first appeared.</p><p>A similar fate could be met by many restaurant companies if they do not take active steps to modernize their businesses and stay relevant with evolving industry and consumer trends.</p><p>Technological innovation and rapid changes in consumer preferences have introduced a near-constant pace of disruption adding to the already complex foodservice industry. </p><p>We’ve assembled some of our most popular insights relative to trends, technology, innovation, and performance optimization to help cut through the noise around some of these issues and give leaders practical advice for not only keeping up with but leapfrogging the competition.</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a98ec8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="a98ec8d" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<style>/*! elementor - v3.7.3 - 29-08-2022 */
.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=".svg"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>					<div class="elementor-image">
												<img width="640" height="211" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends-1024x338.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="restaurant and food trends" loading="lazy" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends-1024x338.jpg 1024w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends-350x116.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends-300x99.jpg 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends-768x254.jpg 768w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/restaurant-and-food-trends.jpg 1314w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" />														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
