				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Restaurant trends are shifting billions of dollars within the $3.5 trillion foodservice industry globally, making and re-shaping categories and segments. They are moving faster than many chains can even comprehend and it’s affecting the competitive landscape across geographies globally — from Canada to the Middle East, India and beyond — and across categories of the industry, from burgers to pizza to steakhouses and casual dining. <a href="https://aaronallen.com/restaurant-trends">Read More</a></p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8fb818c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8fb818c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p><a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-trends-2019"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-13229 size-full" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019.jpg" alt="restaurant trends 2019" width="1314" height="434" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019.jpg 1314w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019-350x116.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019-300x99.jpg 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019-768x254.jpg 768w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-trends-2019-1024x338.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1314px) 100vw, 1314px" /></a></p><p>Volatility. Variance. Disruption. The global foodservice industry is going to have to start responding and performing with the agility and technological savvy of a Silicon Valley startup if it is to maintain its relevance and share of stomach. <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-trends-2019">Read More</a></p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1c9a1cd elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="1c9a1cd" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4783ccc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="4783ccc" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-image">
												<img width="640" height="344" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Restaurant-Innovation-Failures.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Restaurant-Innovation-Failures.jpg 744w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Restaurant-Innovation-Failures-350x188.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Restaurant-Innovation-Failures-300x161-1.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" />														</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c11275e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="c11275e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>The famed Ringling Brothers–Barnum &amp; Bailey Circus closed in January 2017 after almost a century and a half of operation. Its failure to honor its brand&#8217;s DNA — to continue to spark the magic that resonated with audiences for over a century —  proved fatal. Restaurant chains can learn lessons from this powerful story. <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-industry-innovation">Read More</a></p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e3ff209 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="e3ff209" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
				</div>
