				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6b46d1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6b46d1e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p><a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-innovation"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13294" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1.jpg" alt="restaurant innovation" width="1314" height="434" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1.jpg 1314w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1-350x116.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1-300x99.jpg 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1-768x254.jpg 768w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/restaurant-innovation-1-1024x338.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1314px) 100vw, 1314px" /></a></p><p>What was already one of the most complex businesses in the world is becoming even more so following the arrival of the Fourth Industrial Revolution and new consumer demands for convenience. The next five years are going to be more disruptive to the industry than the previous 50. <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-innovation">Read More</a></p>					</div>
