								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p><a href="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-14623" src="https://aaronallen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats.jpg" alt="alternative foodservice formats" width="1314" height="434" srcset="https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats.jpg 1314w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats-350x116.jpg 350w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats-300x99.jpg 300w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats-768x254.jpg 768w, https://11qkih2fw9d2h2oz31jff0fi-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/alternative-foodservice-formats-1024x338.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1314px) 100vw, 1314px" /></a>For as many mentions as you may read in the coming year(s) about alternative proteins and the rise of organics and insect diets,  these are all food — not format — related. It&#8217;s clear the alternative formats shaping up are stealing share from traditional foodservice establishments around the world.  <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/alternative-foodservice-formats">Read More</a></p>					</div>
