				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">If you're a foodservice operator or investor interested in restaurant innovation, seeking to drive growth, optimize performance, maximize value, or create a modernized portfolio in the face of increasing competitive dynamics and an accelerated pace of change, we can help. </h2>		</div>
