					<description><![CDATA[<p>Volatility, variance, disruption, and downright white-knuckle rides await us all in 2019, at least on some level. Whether your company will be up, down, or skidding sideways depends on a variety of variables that we will touch on briefly here. Let us first enjoy (or cringe our way through) a hearty word salad: digital, delivery, &#8230; </p>
