							Change Is Great... <br>You Go First						</h3>
					
											<div class="elementor-flip-box__layer__description">
							While investments in technology, infrastructure, modernization, and diversification generally meet with approval, in other business lines there is still quite a bit of delaying, even dismissing, these initiatives, perhaps revealing a subconscious desire to wait and pilfer from the pioneers.						</div>
					
