											<h3 class="elementor-flip-box__layer__title">
							Safe Hands, Not Smart Hands						</h3>
					
											<div class="elementor-flip-box__layer__description">
							Owners with large portfolios often delegate day-to-day operations to trusted number twos, who may or may not have the operational expertise to see the business through this transition.						</div>
					
								</div>
		</div>
		</div>
		</div>
				</div>
				</div>
						</div>
					</div>
